        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Dug this up..thought I would share</P><P>Prior to Sept 13<BR> - Charm removed<BR> - Screaming terror given, broke, fixed, changed to what it is now<BR> - Pet nerf #1, damage lowered on 49 pet<BR> - Pet nerf #2, damage lowered again on 49 pet to max hitter of 55<BR> - Pet nerf #3, Pet no longer uses delay of weapons</P><P>Sept 13, 1999 - PvP code added..lich bug introduced<BR> - Kiting nerf</P><P>Sept 22, 1999 - <snicker>  cough...ahem... Lich was changed to GIVE more mana...</P><P>Sept 28, 1999 - pets do less damage in PvP</P><P>Dec 1, 1999 - FD nerf</P><P>Dec 14, 1999 - summon corpse added</P><P>Feb 3, 2000 - DMF no longer functions in Sky</P><P>Feb 17, 2000 - Paineel added<BR>   - FD screwed with resulting in after 2 mins FD pet will suicide</P><P>May 12, 2000 - Guards buffed, various necro solo spots nerfed</P><P>Sept 19, 2000 - duck stick quest added</P><P>Nov 29, 2000 - 39+ pets auto dual wield</P><P>Jan 9, 2001 - Root/snare stack</P><P>Other things I couldn't find the exact patch specifically stating<BR> - Pets now have PC dex, rarely proc weapons<BR> - Spectre form now has same negative faction as lich form<BR> - 44+ pets now "lifetap" a pathetic little heal<BR> - 10 Level limit restriction added on lifetaps, no longer immune.  God bosses made specifically immune</P><P><BR>Basically the only "positive" necro only "enhancements" really aren't.</P><P>- Our pets get reduced in return for auto dual wielding lifetapping pets that are a shadow of the former.<BR>- Spells are changed because "as designed" makes us "too powerful"</P><P>That's it.  Look at all the other classes and they all get added features and functionality.  We are the only class which gets this junk and are expected to smile about having Mana Transfer added to our job description while having summoner of ungodly beasty removed.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
